post_content.caption: Zhao Leji: China's initiatives deliver concrete benefits to people
post_content.description:
For  more:
https://news.cgtn.com/news/2024-03-28/Zhao-Leji-China-s-initiatives-deliver-concrete-benefits-to-people-1skQM8tEtNu/p.html

"China has proposed and pursued high quality Belt and Road cooperation, the Global Development Initiative, the Global Security Initiative and the Global Civilization Initiative, contributing a lot to global prosperity and stability and delivering concrete benefits to the people," said Zhao Leji, chairman of the National People's Congress Standing Committee.
He made the remarks in a keynote speech at the opening ceremony of the Boao Forum for Asia Annual Conference 2024 on March 28.
